FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773155490
OL,3,C'Everything costs more', Muslims mark
OL,4,CRamadan amid rising bills and food
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,F"Prices have increased by a
OL,8,Fsignificant amout, we are seeing
OL,9,Fcustomers coming in, but we have lots
OL,10,Fof footfall, they are buying less.
OL,12,F"They used to buy one whole sheep for
OL,13,FRamadan but now they are just buying a
OL,14,Fpart of it."
OL,16,FAcross the UK, rising food prices and
OL,17,Fhousehold bills have forced many
OL,18,Ffamilies to rethink their budgets.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773155490
OL,3,C'Everything costs more', Muslims mark
OL,4,CRamadan amid rising bills and food
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FFor Muslims observing Ramadan, a month
OL,8,Ftraditionally centred around family
OL,9,Fmeals and charity, the pressure is
OL,10,Ffelt even more sharply.
OL,12,FMohima, says the price of every day
OL,13,Ffoods has surged compared to previous
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,F"Last year we bought mangoes for #7.99
OL,17,Fa kilo, now it's gone to #12.99, so
OL,18,Fit's almost doubled in price", she
OL,19,Fadded.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773155490
OL,3,C'Everything costs more', Muslims mark
OL,4,CRamadan amid rising bills and food
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,F"We have minimised out shop, we are
OL,8,Fnow eating less meat and trying to buy
OL,9,Fmore vegetables."
OL,11,FRamadan is not only a time for fasting
OL,12,Ffrom dawn until sunset, it is also a
OL,13,Ftime of giving.
OL,15,FOne of the key pillars of Islam is
OL,16,Fknown as 'Zakat', a form of charitable
OL,17,Fgiving intended to help those most in
OL,18,Fneed.
OL,20,FBut when household budgets are
OL,21,Fstretched, even that becomes difficult.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773155490
OL,3,C'Everything costs more', Muslims mark
OL,4,CRamadan amid rising bills and food
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FAnother customer told ITV News they
OL,8,Fare struggling to give as much as they
OL,9,Fnormally would this year.
OL,11,F"I can't afford to give as much as I
OL,12,Fwant to, there is still time, we all
OL,13,Fgive money to people less well off,
OL,14,Fbut this year it's harder."
OL,16,FFor many in the community, support has
OL,17,Fcome from a local place of worship,
OL,18,Fthe Shahjalal Mosque on Stapleton
OL,19,FRoad, Easton.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
