PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773155490
OL,3,C'Everything costs more', Muslims mark
OL,4,CRamadan amid rising bills and food
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FSince the pandemic and the onset of
OL,8,Fthe cost of living crisis, the mosque
OL,9,Fhad increasingly become a hub for
OL,10,Fpeople seeking warmth, food and
OL,11,Fcommunity.
OL,13,FMohammad Ansiul Islam, the mosque's
OL,14,Fchair, says its doors are open to
OL,15,Feveryone.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773155490
OL,3,C'Everything costs more', Muslims mark
OL,4,CRamadan amid rising bills and food
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,F"The mosque became a community hub
OL,8,Fsince lockdown, when the cost of
OL,9,Fliving crisis hit, we opened the doors
OL,10,Ffor people to come here enjoy the
OL,11,Fwarmth. It's is open to everyone no
OL,12,Fmatter their faith or ethnicity.
OL,14,F"As long as you're hungry, you are
OL,15,Fwelcome".
OL,17,FDuring Ramadan, volunteers help
OL,18,Fprepare meals for those gathering to
OL,19,Fbreak their fast at sunset.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773155490
OL,3,C'Everything costs more', Muslims mark
OL,4,CRamadan amid rising bills and food
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,FRob Moshak, says the initiative has
OL,8,Fgrown steadily in recent years, "This
OL,9,Fis our fifth year, we've served in
OL,10,Fexcess of five thousand meals."
OL,12,F"It's incredible to see us become a
OL,13,Fhelping hand, there's never a 'no',
OL,14,Fpeople are always helped. Everyone is
OL,15,Fgenerous they want to give, the Mosque
OL,16,Fis open to any walk of life, we are
OL,17,Falways open to help."
OL,19,FFor worshipper Zara, the changes
OL,20,Fbrought about by the rising prices are
OL,21,Fnoticeable even at home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773155490
OL,3,C'Everything costs more', Muslims mark
OL,4,CRamadan amid rising bills and food
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,F"When I was younger, I would notice
OL,8,Fmum and dad would bring loads of dates
OL,9,Fhome, now there's only one box.
OL,11,F"When I see the price of food, I feel
OL,12,Fguilty, especially for those people
OL,13,Fwho are less fortunate than us who
OL,14,Fcan't really afford food during this
OL,15,Fmonth."
OL,17,FDespite the financial strain she says
OL,18,Fhelping others remains central to the
OL,19,Fspirt of Ramadan.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773155490
OL,3,C'Everything costs more', Muslims mark
OL,4,CRamadan amid rising bills and food
OL,5,Cprices
OL,7,F"In times of crisis, helping those who
OL,8,Fneed it more really impacts your
OL,9,Fmental health, it makes me happy
OL,10,Fhelping others out."
OL,12,FAs families gathered to break their
OL,13,Ffast, the generosity and warmth of the
OL,14,Fcommunity remain clear.
OL,16,FBut this community, like many others
OL,17,Facross our region and the UK are
OL,18,Fnavigating a cost of living crisis
OL,19,Fthat continues to affect all our
OL,20,Feveryday lives.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
